1
00:00:00,530 --> 00:00:02,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Suppressing the urge to speed off,</i></font>

2
00:00:02,230 --> 00:00:05,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}these 15 drivers focus 
on the drones in front of them,</i></font>

3
00:00:05,780 --> 00:00:08,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}waiting for that light to turn green.</i></font>

4
00:00:09,100 --> 00:00:13,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And the 16, our final competitor, 
passes through the gate!</i></font>

5
00:00:14,420 --> 00:00:15,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And there's the green!</i></font>

6
00:00:18,450 --> 00:00:20,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}It's a picture-perfect start!</i></font>

7
00:00:20,730 --> 00:00:26,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}It's all orderly as the Godly Fifteen
zoom away in single file!</i></font>

8
00:00:26,580 --> 00:00:29,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Sawatari in the 4 car is 
pushing hard from the start,</i></font>

9
00:00:29,810 --> 00:00:32,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}even though his tires will still be cold.</i></font>

10
00:00:32,840 --> 00:00:35,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is likely his strategy.</font>

11
00:00:35,510 --> 00:00:39,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}He's going on the offensive
by flying out of the gate.</i></font>

12
00:00:39,460 --> 00:00:43,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Living up to his reputation, Sawatari 
the gambler risks it all without fear.</i></font>

13
00:00:43,230 --> 00:00:45,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}But will it pay off in the end
 or cost him dearly?</i></font>

14
00:00:46,420 --> 00:00:49,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's no good. 
I still can't stand to watch.</font>

15
00:00:50,470 --> 00:00:52,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Honey, you could at least try.</font>

16
00:00:53,940 --> 00:00:57,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our children are 
working hard in this race.</font>

17
00:00:57,820 --> 00:00:59,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What does it say if we turn away?</font>

18
00:01:00,060 --> 00:01:02,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Our children?</i></font>

19
00:01:06,290 --> 00:01:07,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right.</font>

20
00:01:08,140 --> 00:01:11,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm already so proud 
of Kana-chan and Ren.</font>

21
00:01:12,340 --> 00:01:15,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The 4 car is in the process
 of eking out a lead.</i></font>

22
00:01:16,350 --> 00:01:19,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}How will the two cars 
directly behind him respond?</i></font>

23
00:01:22,500 --> 00:01:24,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}They're nearly at the Hydro Trap.</i></font>

24
00:01:25,350 --> 00:01:27,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The 4 car splashes through it!</i></font>

25
00:01:27,880 --> 00:01:32,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And the size of the spray he's kicking up
 indicates how fast he's going!</i></font>

26
00:01:34,430 --> 00:01:37,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Whoa! The 4 is thrown 
sharply off balance!</i></font>

27
00:01:37,790 --> 00:01:41,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Did his wet tires 
lose purchase on the road?</i></font>

28
00:01:42,160 --> 00:01:45,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Get a grip, Sawatari, 
you utter imbecile.</i></font>

29
00:01:45,340 --> 00:01:47,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The 4 car is spinning out.</i></font>

30
00:01:47,250 --> 00:01:50,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How do I avoid him? Right? Or left?</i></font>

31
00:01:51,090 --> 00:01:52,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Right!</i></font>

32
00:01:51,090 --> 00:01:52,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Right!</i></font>

33
00:01:53,800 --> 00:01:54,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Mistake.</i></font>

34
00:01:57,420 --> 00:01:59,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The 4 car spins out!</font>

35
00:01:59,820 --> 00:02:04,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And with their line blocked, the 12 
and the 86 spin to avoid a collision!</i></font>

36
00:03:33,110 --> 00:03:34,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Impact"><font size="90"><b><font color="#d1082a">MF Ghost</font></b></font></font></font>

37
00:03:35,490 --> 00:03:37,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've never seen chaos like it!</font>

38
00:03:37,940 --> 00:03:39,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's happening out there, folks?</font>

39
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:39,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Arial"><font color="#ff060f">m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100</font></font></b></font>

40
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:43,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Arial">The Strongest
Train</font></b></font>

41
00:03:39,670 --> 00:03:44,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The top three in qualifying
have come to a complete stop!</i></font>

42
00:03:44,110 --> 00:03:46,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}They managed to avoid crashing,</i></font>

43
00:03:46,090 --> 00:03:48,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}but the cars previously behind them
 are now blasting past.</i></font>

44
00:03:49,370 --> 00:03:52,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's a gap between the Lamborghini 
and the red car behind it.</i></font>

45
00:03:52,370 --> 00:03:55,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You know what to do. Go, Katagiri.</i></font>

46
00:04:01,570 --> 00:04:05,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The 86 and the 12 manage
 to get going again!</i></font>

47
00:04:05,710 --> 00:04:10,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Lightning fast as always, 
the pair executed perfect spin turns!</i></font>

48
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:13,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was quite impressive.</font>

49
00:04:13,160 --> 00:04:18,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They recognized there was enough space
 between the 3 and the 18 to squeeze in.</font>

50
00:04:19,310 --> 00:04:23,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Even the slightest hesitation 
would've made it harder to rejoin.</i></font>

51
00:04:23,670 --> 00:04:26,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}They ran the risk of colliding
 with the next car.</i></font>

52
00:04:26,320 --> 00:04:31,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They acted before race control issued 
a directive, which worries me a little.</font>

53
00:04:31,410 --> 00:04:33,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I doubt they'll get a penalty for it.</font>

54
00:04:33,630 --> 00:04:38,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The driver of the 86 seemed 
100% confident in his maneuver,</font>

55
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:41,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and the 12 car spun it around
 pretty much in tandem.</font>

56
00:04:42,410 --> 00:04:48,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think both of them having three-pedal
 manual transmission was key.</font>

57
00:04:48,590 --> 00:04:52,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Being a two-pedal automatic, 
the 4 couldn't pull the same trick.</font>

58
00:04:53,290 --> 00:04:58,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And Sawatari, our polesitter, 
rejoins the race in last place.</i></font>

59
00:04:58,480 --> 00:05:03,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}A mistake like this is hard to imagine 
from a driver like Sawatari Koki.</i></font>

60
00:05:03,860 --> 00:05:05,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}What do you suppose happened?</i></font>

61
00:05:06,150 --> 00:05:11,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I'd say he got on the power a split second 
too early after exiting the trap.</i></font>

62
00:05:12,070 --> 00:05:16,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The wet tires didn't grip the road 
in the way the driver was expecting.</font>

63
00:05:16,950 --> 00:05:21,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}With the adrenaline pumping, 
it wasn't the measured start he needed,</i></font>

64
00:05:21,340 --> 00:05:26,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}and the Hydro Trap was in the perfect place
 to pounce on that nervous energy.</i></font>

65
00:05:27,760 --> 00:05:29,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ah, Ko-kun!</i></font>

66
00:05:29,990 --> 00:05:33,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's been acting differently
since our date yesterday.</i></font>

67
00:05:34,580 --> 00:05:36,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He didn't even finish his lunch.</i></font>

68
00:05:37,100 --> 00:05:41,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}It's the kind of call I doubt he'd make 
if he were in a calm state of mind.</i></font>

69
00:05:41,960 --> 00:05:46,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And it shows the pressure of starting 
on pole and trying to stay out in front.</i></font>

70
00:05:47,100 --> 00:05:49,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>All that pressure must've
been weighing him down.</i></font>

71
00:05:50,070 --> 00:05:51,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My poor Ko-kun.</i></font>

72
00:05:52,260 --> 00:05:56,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll make you feel better later, 
so please come back to me in one piece.</i></font>

73
00:06:01,830 --> 00:06:03,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, what a joke.</font>

74
00:06:04,030 --> 00:06:06,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I never denied being a screwup.</font>

75
00:06:07,430 --> 00:06:10,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Still, that's a huge weight
 off my shoulders now.</i></font>

76
00:06:10,770 --> 00:06:14,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Feels like someone exorcised ten specters
that were clinging to me.</i></font>

77
00:06:14,680 --> 00:06:16,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>All I gotta do now is pass some cars.</i></font>

78
00:06:16,840 --> 00:06:19,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I already got the pole position bonus,</i></font>

79
00:06:19,380 --> 00:06:24,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>so it's time to add to the stack 
by scoring some overtaking bonuses.</i></font>

80
00:06:24,860 --> 00:06:26,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wait for me, Sana.</i></font>

81
00:06:26,730 --> 00:06:29,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Whatever you want, it's yours.</i></font>

82
00:06:30,670 --> 00:06:35,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The Godly Fifteen bear down 
on the hairpin where Sector 1
becomes Sector 2!</i></font>

83
00:06:35,620 --> 00:06:38,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Let's take a look at the order
 at this juncture.</i></font>

84
00:06:38,480 --> 00:06:40,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}In the lead, it's Moroboshi in the 885.</i></font>

85
00:06:41,200 --> 00:06:44,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}In second, it's Emma Greene in the 624.</i></font>

86
00:06:44,640 --> 00:06:46,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Akaba is third in the 2 car.</i></font>

87
00:06:46,650 --> 00:06:48,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Aiba is fourth in the 9.</i></font>

88
00:06:48,470 --> 00:06:50,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Fifth, Yanagida in the 6.</i></font>

89
00:06:50,430 --> 00:06:52,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Sixth, Ishigami in the 1 car.</i></font>

90
00:06:52,340 --> 00:06:54,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Seventh, Maezono in the 13.</i></font>

91
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:56,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Eighth, Oishi in the 3 car.</i></font>

92
00:06:56,970 --> 00:07:00,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And here, back in ninth place, 
it's Katagiri in the 86.</i></font>

93
00:07:00,850 --> 00:07:03,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Tenth belongs to Beckenbauer in the 12.</i></font>

94
00:07:03,110 --> 00:07:07,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}These two still have plenty of the race left
to climb up through the field.</i></font>

95
00:07:07,730 --> 00:07:10,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And I have no doubts over
whether they've given up.</i></font>

96
00:07:10,510 --> 00:07:14,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}These red and white bullets 
have explosive potential!</i></font>

97
00:07:15,080 --> 00:07:19,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}In 11th, it's Kitahara in the 18.
In 12th, it's Sakamoto in the 5.</i></font>

98
00:07:19,290 --> 00:07:21,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}13th belongs to Taylor in the 8.</i></font>

99
00:07:21,220 --> 00:07:23,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}In 14th, it's Yashio in the 16.</i></font>

100
00:07:23,520 --> 00:07:27,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And the 4 car is already 
hot on their heels!</i></font>

101
00:07:27,650 --> 00:07:32,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Being able to rejoin the race without 
damaging the car is paying off big-time.</font>

102
00:07:33,100 --> 00:07:38,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}That's Sawatari Koki in his blue bullet,
one of MFG's famous tricolor racers!</i></font>

103
00:07:38,240 --> 00:07:42,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}How far can he climb up 
the field? Let's watch.</i></font>

104
00:07:46,060 --> 00:07:48,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My mind's gone blank.</i></font>

105
00:07:48,510 --> 00:07:51,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've lost my pacemaker.</i></font>

106
00:07:52,700 --> 00:07:56,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Booth to Sena. You're wrecking your tires. 
This race has six laps, remember.</font>

107
00:07:56,700 --> 00:07:57,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Rein it in!</i></font>

108
00:07:58,210 --> 00:08:00,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I would if I could, damn it.</i></font>

109
00:08:01,110 --> 00:08:03,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't know how to set the freaking pace.</i></font>

110
00:08:04,540 --> 00:08:06,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you think of my pace? 
Am I going too slow?</font>

111
00:08:06,880 --> 00:08:09,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Obviously not. Stay confident.</i></font>

112
00:08:09,580 --> 00:08:11,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So I'm not going slow?</i></font>

113
00:08:11,750 --> 00:08:15,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Despite the fact the Aston's 
breathing down my neck?</i></font>

114
00:08:15,870 --> 00:08:19,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The whole world is watching me 
lead the pack right now.</i></font>

115
00:08:19,960 --> 00:08:24,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My Gunma pride won't </i>let<i> me
 drive like a chump.</i></font>

116
00:08:26,110 --> 00:08:27,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What's going on?</i></font>

117
00:08:27,190 --> 00:08:30,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Something about the 885 makes it
 easy to stick close to him.</i></font>

118
00:08:31,150 --> 00:08:34,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's like he has something in common
 with Mr. Fujiwara's driving.</i></font>

119
00:08:34,740 --> 00:08:37,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I think it might be the rhythm.</i></font>

120
00:08:37,700 --> 00:08:39,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I could pass if I wanted,</i></font>

121
00:08:39,470 --> 00:08:42,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but there's something to be said 
for seeing how this plays out.</i></font>

122
00:08:43,050 --> 00:08:46,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The race has only just begun, 
and it's going to be a long one.</i></font>

123
00:08:46,500 --> 00:08:48,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll be patient for now.</i></font>

124
00:08:48,460 --> 00:08:50,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Because I know you'll be back.</i></font>

125
00:08:51,330 --> 00:08:53,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And you're the one 
I want to battle, darling.</i></font>

126
00:08:55,260 --> 00:08:59,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The Godly Fifteen scythe through 
the forested area of Sector 2.</i></font>

127
00:08:59,100 --> 00:09:03,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And just look at those big numbers
unexpectedly occupying first and second.</i></font>

128
00:09:03,910 --> 00:09:08,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Being at the head of the pack 
comes with any number of stresses.</i></font>

129
00:09:08,130 --> 00:09:11,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Gotta wonder if it's too much
 for a rookie like Moroboshi.</i></font>

130
00:09:11,800 --> 00:09:15,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This might've turned into 
a stroke of luck for Kanata.</font>

131
00:09:16,090 --> 00:09:18,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His biggest rivals are behind him,</font>

132
00:09:18,890 --> 00:09:21,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and the top two are rookies,
lacking in experience.</font>

133
00:09:21,770 --> 00:09:23,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This could be a real opportunity, right?</font>

134
00:09:23,930 --> 00:09:26,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If he's able to climb up
through the field...</font>

135
00:09:26,130 --> 00:09:30,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's one way of looking at it, 
but you're forgetting one vital thing.</font>

136
00:09:30,620 --> 00:09:33,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Beckenbauer is the 
"absolute king" for a reason,</font>

137
00:09:33,210 --> 00:09:36,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and it remains to be seen what he'll do 
now that he's right on our tail.</font>

138
00:09:37,530 --> 00:09:42,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The sunny yellow Supra and the dark green 
Aston Martin emerge from the shade.</i></font>

139
00:09:42,180 --> 00:09:45,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And a bright red Ferrari 
is honing in on them.</i></font>

140
00:09:45,480 --> 00:09:49,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Our colorful top three are 
coming up to the Jumping Spot.</i></font>

141
00:09:50,150 --> 00:09:52,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}This seems a good moment to ask, Sudo-san.</i></font>

142
00:09:53,070 --> 00:09:57,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Jumps are a bit of a rarity 
in the world of racing...</i></font>

143
00:09:57,460 --> 00:10:02,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...aside from in rally, which often 
takes place on mountainous courses.</font>

144
00:10:02,390 --> 00:10:06,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As a rally driver yourself, could you give us
 some insight on how to take jumps?</font>

145
00:10:07,120 --> 00:10:09,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I understand. I can certainly try.</font>

146
00:10:10,050 --> 00:10:12,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Since this is 
a man-made jump,</i></font>

147
00:10:12,780 --> 00:10:15,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}it's a bit different from 
the kind you find in nature.</i></font>

148
00:10:15,760 --> 00:10:19,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}But in general, it's about 
controlling where and how 
you're going to land.</i></font>

149
00:10:20,120 --> 00:10:23,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The last thing you want 
to do is lose speed 
or hit the brakes.</i></font>

150
00:10:23,660 --> 00:10:29,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}If you're tipped forward 
when you land, 
you'll be thrown off balance.</i></font>

151
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:32,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}That'll prevent you 
from braking in time 
for the next right turn,</i></font>

152
00:10:32,540 --> 00:10:34,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}and risks sending you 
out of the course.</i></font>

153
00:10:35,310 --> 00:10:40,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The crucial thing is to grip the wheel
 and try to touch down level.</font>

154
00:10:40,600 --> 00:10:45,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}If you start rotating in the air, 
you'll be all over the place when you land,</i></font>

155
00:10:45,490 --> 00:10:50,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}and as you struggle to regain control,
you're at risk of spinning or crashing.</i></font>

156
00:10:50,690 --> 00:10:53,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So in general, grip the wheel,
 don't touch the brakes,</font>

157
00:10:53,360 --> 00:10:55,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and keep the gas pedal half down.</font>

158
00:10:55,740 --> 00:10:59,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The more you explain it, the more 
dangerous and difficult it sounds.</font>

159
00:10:59,420 --> 00:11:01,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's pretty tough to verbalize it.</font>

160
00:11:01,960 --> 00:11:07,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}But I imagine these 15 elite drivers 
are able to handle it all intuitively.</i></font>

161
00:11:07,820 --> 00:11:10,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The leaders are now 
on the run-up to the jump.</i></font>

162
00:11:11,190 --> 00:11:13,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The jumping-off point awaits.</i></font>

163
00:11:17,310 --> 00:11:19,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}This legion of supercars takes to the air!</i></font>

164
00:11:19,810 --> 00:11:24,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}An incredible sight! It's Double Lane's
 specialty, the Jumping Spot!</i></font>

165
00:11:24,060 --> 00:11:27,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}You won't see a race like this 
anywhere else in the world!</i></font>

166
00:11:28,580 --> 00:11:30,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Here's the duo in the spotlight.</i></font>

167
00:11:30,890 --> 00:11:33,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The 12 is still clinging to the 86's rear,</i></font>

168
00:11:33,580 --> 00:11:36,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}putting unrelenting pressure 
on Katagiri Kanata!</i></font>

169
00:11:37,260 --> 00:11:39,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is what I was talking about.</font>

170
00:11:39,640 --> 00:11:42,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With Beckenbauer on his tail,</font>

171
00:11:42,140 --> 00:11:44,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Katagiri-kun can't make a move
 even if he wants to.</font>

172
00:11:44,800 --> 00:11:47,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His overtaking options 
have been reduced.</font>

173
00:11:48,190 --> 00:11:52,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If he tries to pull ahead, he creates 
an opening for the car behind him.</font>

174
00:11:53,020 --> 00:11:57,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whether he goes to the inside or 
the outside, he'll always leave a gap.</font>

175
00:11:57,980 --> 00:12:00,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's definitely bad news.</font>

176
00:12:01,480 --> 00:12:05,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A driver like Beckenbauer 
won't miss that kind of chance.</font>

177
00:12:05,400 --> 00:12:09,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even with their inherent speed, 
if this pair are stuck in a stalemate,</font>

178
00:12:09,460 --> 00:12:11,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it'll be hard for them to move forward.</font>

179
00:12:13,010 --> 00:12:16,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But there's something about how 
the 12 is moving that bothers me.</i></font>

180
00:12:17,500 --> 00:12:18,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Would he actually try that?</i></font>

181
00:12:22,280 --> 00:12:23,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}MF Ghost.</i></font>

182
00:12:27,290 --> 00:12:28,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}MF Ghost.</i></font>

183
00:12:35,370 --> 00:12:37,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Mr. Beckenbauer.</i></font>

184
00:12:37,550 --> 00:12:40,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I sense no intent to pass from you.</i></font>

185
00:12:41,240 --> 00:12:46,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You're maintaining the exact distance
 that will maximize the tow.</i></font>

186
00:12:46,860 --> 00:12:49,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>With you occupying the draft
 directly behind me,</i></font>

187
00:12:49,800 --> 00:12:52,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>the 86 is accelerating smoothly.</i></font>

188
00:12:53,080 --> 00:12:56,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can tell my top speed is above 
what I'd reach if I were on my own.</i></font>

189
00:12:57,000 --> 00:13:00,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Are you actually helping me?</i></font>

190
00:13:01,030 --> 00:13:03,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If you are, I gratefully accept the aid.</i></font>

191
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:06,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll switch to pursuit mode now.
 Do try to keep up.</i></font>

192
00:13:09,460 --> 00:13:12,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's stopped trying to block me.
 Seems I got through to him.</i></font>

193
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:15,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's surprisingly quick on the uptake.</i></font>

194
00:13:15,500 --> 00:13:18,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This gentleman's agreement 
is a win-win for both of us.</i></font>

195
00:13:18,120 --> 00:13:19,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Let's see what you've got.</i></font>

196
00:13:19,820 --> 00:13:22,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Eyes forward, Katagiri.</i></font>

197
00:13:25,820 --> 00:13:28,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, fantastic. That nightmare, 
Katagiri, is right behind me.</i></font>

198
00:13:28,980 --> 00:13:31,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And behind him is someone 
even worse: the crazy German.</i></font>

199
00:13:32,520 --> 00:13:36,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How bad can things get? 
What did I do to deserve this?</i></font>

200
00:13:37,290 --> 00:13:39,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It feels like my life's on the line.</i></font>

201
00:13:43,470 --> 00:13:44,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Again with this?</i></font>

202
00:13:45,430 --> 00:13:48,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why am I never able to hold him at bay?</i></font>

203
00:13:49,430 --> 00:13:51,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Huh. An interesting choice.</i></font>

204
00:13:52,330 --> 00:13:54,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}There's movement 
in the middle of the pack!</i></font>

205
00:13:54,700 --> 00:13:57,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The 86 is going on the attack!</i></font>

206
00:14:01,310 --> 00:14:05,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Damn it. The Porsche is making 
a move while I'm still all at sea.</i></font>

207
00:14:06,010 --> 00:14:10,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And I'm supposed to take on these monsters
 at the corner into Sector 3?</i></font>

208
00:14:10,570 --> 00:14:12,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's not worth the risk.</i></font>

209
00:14:14,840 --> 00:14:17,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And here comes the 18!</i></font>

210
00:14:17,680 --> 00:14:19,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A third one? Seriously?</i></font>

211
00:14:20,020 --> 00:14:23,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Screw you, Kitahara.
You're not going anywhere.</i></font>

212
00:14:23,460 --> 00:14:27,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Once I get my nose in there, 
I don't back down from endurance tests.</i></font>

213
00:14:27,860 --> 00:14:30,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}This is turning into 
something incredible.</i></font>

214
00:14:30,140 --> 00:14:32,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}A sequence of side-by-side battles.</i></font>

215
00:14:32,500 --> 00:14:36,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The 3 car is under relentless attack!</i></font>

216
00:14:36,480 --> 00:14:39,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Katagiri Kanata 
was the first to strike,</i></font>

217
00:14:39,590 --> 00:14:44,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}followed by the 12 car, 
and now the 18 is taking advantage!</i></font>

218
00:14:47,220 --> 00:14:51,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}But the 3 car is fighting back!
The bumpy road's a struggle for its tires.</i></font>

219
00:14:52,920 --> 00:14:57,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}It's a desperate cornering battle 
as they both fight to maintain balance.</i></font>

220
00:14:58,580 --> 00:15:02,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I keep hitting the biggest bumps
 for some reason.</i></font>

221
00:15:02,770 --> 00:15:05,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The 3 car is starting to be outdragged.</i></font>

222
00:15:05,240 --> 00:15:08,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Kitahara in the 18 zooms off in front!</i></font>

223
00:15:08,590 --> 00:15:13,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Oishi in the 3 car has 
just lost three positions!</i></font>

224
00:15:13,090 --> 00:15:15,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}What a shocking display.</i></font>

225
00:15:15,330 --> 00:15:18,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Could you talk us through 
what we just saw, Sudo-san?</i></font>

226
00:15:18,430 --> 00:15:25,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The 86 created an opening which must've 
been extremely painful for Oishi-kun.</font>

227
00:15:25,560 --> 00:15:29,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}When cars go side by side, 
it always slows both of them a little,</i></font>

228
00:15:29,400 --> 00:15:32,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}creating the perfect opening 
for the cars behind.</i></font>

229
00:15:32,410 --> 00:15:35,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that's all the space they need.</font>

230
00:15:39,400 --> 00:15:43,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>When was the last time 
we duked it out, Sawatari?</i></font>

231
00:15:44,130 --> 00:15:47,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We never seem to get to
 mix it up while racing.</i></font>

232
00:15:47,700 --> 00:15:51,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We're both driving cars with 
nimbleness as a selling point.</i></font>

233
00:15:51,150 --> 00:15:53,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Don't expect me to just lie down.</i></font>

234
00:15:53,510 --> 00:15:55,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Bring it on, Alpine.</i></font>

235
00:15:56,430 --> 00:15:58,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I think it was two seasons ago now?</i></font>

236
00:15:59,270 --> 00:16:04,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I recall you and your sis giving me trouble
 with your barely legal blocking.</i></font>

237
00:16:04,650 --> 00:16:07,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But on your own? I have nothing to fear.</i></font>

238
00:16:07,270 --> 00:16:09,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Where </i>is<i> your talented sister, anyway?</i></font>

239
00:16:10,010 --> 00:16:11,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Did she leave you in the dust?</i></font>

240
00:16:12,130 --> 00:16:15,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If I remember right, 
she always was better than you.</i></font>

241
00:16:19,370 --> 00:16:22,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You're making a move here?
Talk about forcing the issue.</i></font>

242
00:16:22,830 --> 00:16:24,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Bad choice, Yashio.</i></font>

243
00:16:24,740 --> 00:16:26,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You don't look steady at all.</i></font>

244
00:16:27,390 --> 00:16:29,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}We're seeing movement
 at the back now!</i></font>

245
00:16:29,590 --> 00:16:31,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And the 4 car goes for it!</i></font>

246
00:16:32,830 --> 00:16:34,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}He's pulling ahead!</i></font>

247
00:16:34,470 --> 00:16:37,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Sawatari in the 4 climbs up a spot!</i></font>

248
00:16:38,440 --> 00:16:40,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The tricolor musketeers 
are all making moves.</i></font>

249
00:16:40,730 --> 00:16:43,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Was this simply fated to happen?</i></font>

250
00:16:43,100 --> 00:16:48,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}We're seeing the beginning of their quest 
to reclaim their original spots.</i></font>

251
00:16:49,420 --> 00:16:50,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Now, we go back up front.</i></font>

252
00:16:50,730 --> 00:16:54,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}They exit Sector 3 and 
head back along the shoreline.</i></font>

253
00:16:54,270 --> 00:16:56,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}We're into the second lap of the race!</i></font>

254
00:16:58,050 --> 00:17:03,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And now, a question for 
Big Sis Kyoko and Number Seven.</font>

255
00:17:03,270 --> 00:17:07,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Any sweet memories of summer break 
to share? We'll start with Big Sis.</font>

256
00:17:07,350 --> 00:17:09,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mine was awful.</font>

257
00:17:09,860 --> 00:17:12,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I got hit with norovirus 
after eating some raw fish,</font>

258
00:17:12,950 --> 00:17:14,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and I felt like I was gonna die.</font>

259
00:17:15,100 --> 00:17:18,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had killer runs and puked up a storm.</font>

260
00:17:18,200 --> 00:17:20,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was basically trapped
 in the bathroom.</font>

261
00:17:20,890 --> 00:17:22,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Big Sis Kyoko.</font>

262
00:17:22,390 --> 00:17:26,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know being self-effacing is kind of 
your thing, but isn't that a bit overboard?</font>

263
00:17:26,900 --> 00:17:29,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not a joke.</font>

264
00:17:29,000 --> 00:17:31,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you want me to say? 
What happened, happened.</font>

265
00:17:32,090 --> 00:17:37,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That said, I lost 4 kg and my waist shrunk,
 so I'm looking even finer than usual.</font>

266
00:17:37,530 --> 00:17:40,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Moving on from that, uh, 
scatological anecdote...</font>

267
00:17:40,360 --> 00:17:44,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">On to something hopefully a <i>bit</i> more 
glamorous. Take it away, Number Seven.</font>

268
00:17:45,210 --> 00:17:49,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I, uh, had a lot of fun, honestly.</font>

269
00:17:49,550 --> 00:17:51,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I went to visit my grandma in Niigata,</font>

270
00:17:51,920 --> 00:17:55,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and it was like taking 
a trip back to my childhood.</font>

271
00:17:55,520 --> 00:17:57,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stuff like that is so enjoyable.</font>

272
00:17:57,950 --> 00:18:00,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I went to a fireworks display
 in a yukata, too.</font>

273
00:18:01,720 --> 00:18:04,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was all clichéd summery stuff, 
but that didn't ruin it.</font>

274
00:18:04,720 --> 00:18:07,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd say it was a special one for me.</font>

275
00:18:07,410 --> 00:18:12,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Perfect. Exactly the kind of 
idealized picture I was hoping for.</i></font>

276
00:18:12,320 --> 00:18:14,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've never heard two 
more contrasting answers.</font>

277
00:18:14,570 --> 00:18:16,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Downright chaotic.</font>

278
00:18:21,460 --> 00:18:25,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Beckenbauer and Kanata? 
Talk about a scary combo.</i></font>

279
00:18:25,730 --> 00:18:29,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No planning. No practice. 
They're improvising this dance.</i></font>

280
00:18:29,880 --> 00:18:33,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I guess crazy stuff happens
when you put a pair of geniuses together.</i></font>

281
00:18:33,550 --> 00:18:35,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>With my brother way at the back,</i></font>

282
00:18:36,100 --> 00:18:39,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>my best hope is to take advantage 
of their impromptu teaming up.</i></font>

283
00:18:39,560 --> 00:18:43,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Oh! And now the fight over seventh
looks ready to spark into life.</i></font>

284
00:18:43,560 --> 00:18:46,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So fast. Since when has 
his car been that fast?</i></font>

285
00:18:48,890 --> 00:18:50,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And there he goes!</i></font>

286
00:18:50,730 --> 00:18:53,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}He slips through a narrow gap
like an expertly fired shot.</i></font>

287
00:18:53,630 --> 00:18:56,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The red bullet moniker is 
growing more and more accurate.</i></font>

288
00:18:58,700 --> 00:19:01,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I get it. That's why 
he's going faster than usual.</i></font>

289
00:19:02,030 --> 00:19:04,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's the slipstream with the 12 car.</i></font>

290
00:19:05,030 --> 00:19:08,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The physical evidence 
is pretty clear-cut.</i></font>

291
00:19:09,290 --> 00:19:12,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Not that I don't have 
</i>other<i> things to complain about.</i></font>

292
00:19:13,030 --> 00:19:18,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Could you maybe stop zipping past me the 
first chance you get when you're in range?</i></font>

293
00:19:18,380 --> 00:19:21,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Do you never weigh up the situation? 
Or hesitate? Anything like that?</i></font>

294
00:19:22,600 --> 00:19:25,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It helps to be mentally prepared
 when you're being passed, you know.</i></font>

295
00:19:27,420 --> 00:19:29,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And what's more...</i></font>

296
00:19:29,490 --> 00:19:34,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How come the usually aloof 
absolute king is willing to assist you?</i></font>

297
00:19:34,900 --> 00:19:37,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's downright unfair.</i></font>

298
00:19:37,030 --> 00:19:41,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Since when did you two 
become best buddies?</i></font>

299
00:19:41,280 --> 00:19:43,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The 86 car pulls ahead.</i></font>

300
00:19:43,780 --> 00:19:46,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And the 12 follows him through.</i></font>

301
00:19:46,250 --> 00:19:49,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}It's another string of 
side-by-side action!</i></font>

302
00:19:49,850 --> 00:19:53,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They haven't given the NSX 
enough space to steady itself.</i></font>

303
00:19:54,310 --> 00:19:58,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I gotta make my move now.
 Before the gap closes.</i></font>

304
00:20:02,020 --> 00:20:04,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The 18 car follows suit!</i></font>

305
00:20:04,670 --> 00:20:09,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Expertly executed! We're seeing some 
intelligent and efficient racing today.</i></font>

306
00:20:09,510 --> 00:20:13,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'd have a hard time pulling ahead 
of an NSX in a straight-up drag race.</i></font>

307
00:20:14,220 --> 00:20:18,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But right now, my car's inside 
an invisible air tunnel.</i></font>

308
00:20:18,730 --> 00:20:20,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Here's hoping it pulls me along.</i></font>

309
00:20:21,220 --> 00:20:22,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Let me pass him.</i></font>

310
00:20:23,900 --> 00:20:25,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Is he going to fall behind?</i></font>

311
00:20:25,990 --> 00:20:31,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The high-IQ driver, Maezono, 
painfully loses three places!</i></font>

312
00:20:32,460 --> 00:20:35,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm speechless at this point, Sudo-san.</font>

313
00:20:35,780 --> 00:20:38,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This course really is 
seeing incredible speeds.</font>

314
00:20:38,120 --> 00:20:42,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Double Lane is living up
 to its reputation.</font>

315
00:20:42,410 --> 00:20:46,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The battle with air resistance is having 
a bigger effect than anyone thought.</font>

316
00:20:46,720 --> 00:20:48,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even so...</font>

317
00:20:48,790 --> 00:20:51,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Kitahara in the 18 is 
turning into a dark horse,</i></font>

318
00:20:51,640 --> 00:20:53,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}pulling out a performance
 no one expected.</i></font>

319
00:20:54,690 --> 00:21:00,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I had to describe it, I'd call it a twist
 born out of a string of coincidences.</font>

320
00:21:00,670 --> 00:21:07,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}First, these two cars rejoined the race 
right in front of the 18 after spinning.</i></font>

321
00:21:08,110 --> 00:21:11,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Second, there's the fact 
it's only the second lap,</i></font>

322
00:21:11,290 --> 00:21:14,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}so there hasn't been
 much field spread yet.</i></font>

323
00:21:14,570 --> 00:21:19,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Because of that, she's able to keep pace
 with the cars in front of her.</i></font>

324
00:21:20,470 --> 00:21:21,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And third,</i></font>

325
00:21:21,930 --> 00:21:26,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Kitahara Nozomi has always specialized 
in coordinated attacks.</i></font>

326
00:21:26,950 --> 00:21:29,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The pair in front are executing
 some high-level teamwork,</i></font>

327
00:21:29,740 --> 00:21:32,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}but her experience lets her join in.</i></font>

328
00:21:33,450 --> 00:21:37,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I have to admit, it's strange how well
 the 18 is able to follow them.</i></font>

329
00:21:38,100 --> 00:21:44,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}But just look at what the 86 and 
12 cars are capable of together.</i></font>

330
00:21:44,480 --> 00:21:46,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}It's downright incredible.</i></font>

331
00:21:46,990 --> 00:21:50,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Is there any driver out there capable 
of outrunning this pair as allies?</i></font>

332
00:21:51,200 --> 00:21:53,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}They're the strongest train.</i></font>

333
00:23:32,930 --> 00:23:37,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Next time, Turn 36: The Midair Feint.</i></font>

